 exactly what she was doing."],[7533,7687,"Mr. Davis, you can't let this slide."],[7966,8112,"Let's clean that mouth of yours."],[8133,8254,"No, no, please, there's, there's-"],[8254,8395,"Stop, that stuff is toxic!"],[8458,8608,"Actions have consequences."],[8616,8691,"Maybe this time"],[8691,8820,"they'll learn their place."],[9783,9854,"Mr. Davis,"],[9883,10004,"look what she did to me."],[10083,10204,"You fucking bitch."],[10204,10279,"Take it off."],[10387,10450,"Your shirt."],[10462,10608,"Take it off and give it to Linda now."],[10837,10920,"No."]],"6":[[1166,1250,"Relax."],[1291,1416,"I don't undress women."],[1462,1587,"They do it themselves."],[2408,2462,"Fine."],[2550,2641,"You won't strip?"],[2716,2875,"Then your father here can enjoy prison"],[2875,2979,"for sexual harassment."],[3450,3608,"911, what's your emergency?"],[3608,3700,"Mr. Davis, wait."],[3891,3950,"I'll..."],[4208,4275,"I'll do it."],[4275,4379,"No, don't do this."],[4379,4479,"Dad, stop. -No, please, don't."],[4479,4541,"Stop."],[4712,4800,"That's more like it."],[4929,5041,"If it wasn't for Mr. Davis"],[5041,5129,"bringing it up,"],[5229,5350,"as if I'd even want your"],[5350,5483,"raggedy clothes."],[5837,6054,"Mr. Davis, please, please,"],[6087,6195,"please have mercy."],[6341,6425,"Please."],[6604,6733,"I'll do it, anything."],[6754,6845,"You're begging me? -Anything"],[6925,7020,"And who are you?"],[7091,7179,"Seriously."],[7208,7358,"Stop acting like this is some touching"],[7358,7491,"father-daughter moment."],[7683,7750,"Hurry up!"],[7762,7916,"Mr. Davis doesn't have all day."],[7916,7966,"Stop."],[7991,8091,"No, please stop."],[8125,8166,"Please."],[8179,8241,"No, it's-"],[8241,8387,"Please, I'm begging."],[8425,8558,"Please, Mr. Davis."],[8575,8633,"Please."],[8666,8791,"Stay down!"],[9104,9204,"Enough!"]],"7":[[20,95,"Enough!"],[1287,1345,"Evelyn,"],[1370,1450,"what are you doing here?"],[1637,1850,"Bob, is this how you run things at work?"],[1870,2008,"This creep was harassing