putting toothpaste on it will help."],[8504,8575,"Daddy!"],[8575,8637,"It's okay."],[8637,8741,"I got you, buddy."],[8775,8950,"Yeah, you got a little bit of a burn here."],[8975,9104,"All right, hold still."],[9104,9204,"And this,"],[9204,9429,"this is gonna help with the sting, okay?"],[9550,9633,"There you go."],[9704,9754,"How is that?"],[9754,9866,"Does that feel better?"],[9983,10050,"Yeah."],[10054,10112,"Come here."],[10220,10275,"All right."],[10341,10429,"You'll be okay."],[10525,10608,"That's my boy."],[11375,11445,"Dad."]],"12":[[62,112,"Dad."],[258,391,"Mr. Davis, what do you mean?"],[408,470,"How could this man"],[470,583,"possibly be your father?"],[920,1108,"How dare you boss me around?"],[1108,1183,"Exactly."],[1183,1300,"Just because you were invited here"],[1300,1420,"doesn't mean you're worth anything."],[1420,1516,"I'm so sorry, Mr. Davis."],[1516,1637,"Please, please don't be angry."],[1637,1787,"I'll, I'll clean up right away."],[1879,1916,"Okay."],[2262,2312,"Here."],[2379,2475,"Let me help you cool it down."],[2550,2629,"I'll call the doctor."],[2850,2941,"Forget that."],[2966,3070,"Get me toothpaste."],[3083,3154,"What?"],[3204,3375,"You're actually gonna trust him?"],[3375,3500,"Did I fucking stutter?"],[3591,3758,"Somebody get Mr. Davis toothpaste."],[3779,3858,"Now!"],[4270,4375,"This is ridiculous."],[4400,4508,"Just fucking do it."],[5320,5375,"Wait."],[5425,5575,"Did that actually work?"],[5683,5795,"Where did you learn that?"],[5987,6070,"Nobody told me, sir."],[6070,6262,"It's, it's just an old trick."],[6320,6537,"Just something that people my age know."],[7041,7158,"Yeah, if my dad were still alive,"],[7158,7279,"he'd be about your age."],[7562,7675,"Mr. Davis,"],[7758,7875,"please don't lose hope."],[7970,8108,"If your dad is out there,"],[8137,8333,"he's gonna find his way back to you."],[8408,8570,"That, that bond, that bond,"],[8670,8766,"it never fades."]],"13":[[466,541,"Shut up!"],[662,854,"Talk about my dad one more time,"